@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000

### Peticiones sin TOKEN

### Obtener todos los autores
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/authors

### Obtener autor por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/authors/1

### Crear un nuevo autor
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/authors
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "John Doe",
    "email": "john.doe@example.com",
    "bio": "Technical writer and journalist",
    "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### Actualizar un autor
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/authors/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "John Doe Updated",
    "email": "john.updated@example.com",
    "bio": "Senior Technical Writer and Editor",
    "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### Eliminar un autor físicamente
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/authors/1

### Eliminar un autor lógicamente (cambiar status a INACTIVE)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/authors/1/logic
